程序包 org.janusgraph.core.log

接口 ChangeState

public interface ChangeState
Container interface for a set of changes against the graph caused by a particular transaction. This is passed as an argument to ChangeProcessor.process(org.janusgraph.core.JanusGraphTransaction, TransactionId, ChangeState) for the user to retrieve changed elements and act upon it.
作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
